l the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"}]}